{"tid":1550734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"左膠標準處理方法","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T05:48:46.000Z","uid":33307,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"be1e1ba0be49ac15d5560df4ab3f272e8a5a9c66","tid":1550734,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:22:58.000Z","msg":"首先唔好理佢係唔係同路人<br />\n第一就係要搵一個人拉走佢<br />\n第二之後就研究下佢係邊個（敵方臥底？真心左膠？）<br />\n<br />\n就ok，輕鬆<br />\n<br />\n毋需討論太多又話咩要割左膠<br />\n做到以上已經搞掂"},{"pid":"1ff69aa33de4db55ec3d24771c4c9be2c061fda7","tid":1550734,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:23:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b8c2ac57a5febf09a15892d62fb056cce1cdd30","tid":1550734,"uid":254558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:23:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1550636/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1550636/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"68e6703bf9beb7685bd1904e4f39b9ac3364227e","tid":1550734,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:23:47.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我警告你班仆街！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽日啲<span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國旗</span>唔好周圍掉！<br />\n路邊見到唔該即刻幫手執返！<br />\n完咗活動攞返屋企收藏！</span></span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evxvjtB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevxvjtB.jpg&h=73325a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 快啲聽熟加背歌詞，<br />\n唱得莊嚴啲！</span>\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=abf542f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n分段背易啲背：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Oh, say can you see,</span></span><br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">What so proudly we hailed,</span><br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Whose broad stripes and bright stars,</span><br />\nThrough the perilous fight,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">O'er the ramparts we watched,</span><br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And the rocket's red glare,</span><br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Gave proof through the night,</span><br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,</span><br />\n<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.</div><br />\n<br />\n聽日見！</span>"},{"pid":"35a8e51a0e2230b9a5c9e081bfbce041454c64f2","tid":1550734,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:25:02.000Z","msg":"左膠係對抗爭不利既因素<br />\n唔割蓆不過都照打埋"},{"pid":"2f16395a1c01c25efda67b2a38098ba0290dd2ac","tid":1550734,"uid":63757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:25:40.000Z","msg":"打柒左膠啦"},{"pid":"f460b9f335b23399889fccb2d15635dec953e2b0","tid":1550734,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f16395a1c01c25efda67b2a38098ba0290dd2ac","tid":1550734,"uid":63757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:25:40.000Z","msg":"打柒左膠啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:27:21.000Z","msg":"唔好群眾打群眾<br />\n畫面完全無利<br />\n只會顯示示威者內控"},{"pid":"33a8fcc7137da338da624f59367699eea20e7763","tid":1550734,"uid":55638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:28:28.000Z","msg":"召喚7.1 立法會門前勇武撲倒白頭佬gif"},{"pid":"8550c4b0c1e41563d18fd2fe8f6eb85a0302758c","tid":1550734,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35a8e51a0e2230b9a5c9e081bfbce041454c64f2","tid":1550734,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:25:02.000Z","msg":"左膠係對抗爭不利既因素<br />\n唔割蓆不過都照打埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:28:33.000Z","msg":"係不利因數，所以要拉走，在研究身分<br />\n千期唔好鏡頭前打類似自己人既人"},{"pid":"25bd972fb5cf025a36fc0540e6e399c484e74237","tid":1550734,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:28:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不要說 「 左膠 」<br />\n<br />\n試着說 「 藍絲臥底 」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阻人嗰啲藍絲扮架，支持送中，支持警察架"},{"pid":"b4105cc75aac8984b99c1ed87425809882f482b6","tid":1550734,"uid":65409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:29:14.000Z","msg":"今時今日都左膠到<br />\n咁撚大愛 你唔好出去做比人打嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4ff7c24b59ee0f5ff302ad6d6fd11be10c0b0d","tid":1550734,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:29:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\